text.tspan: Please follow the steps below when using the laser.
All lines in Adobe Illustrator are the correct color and width (width must be 0.001 in).
To etch, lines must be in black (R:0 G:0 B:0). To cut, lines must be in red (R:255
Material thickness has been specified. For birch from the Nolop shop, the thickness is 3mm.
You can use calipers to measure other materials' thicknesses.
Material type has been specified for wood or plastic.
Bed height has been set to focus laser.
Manual control (speed + power) when setting material has been checked.
For wood, Power: 100% Speed: 15%. For acrylic, Power: 100% Speed: 8%.
The position of the cuts on the workpiece is correct. Remember to check both corners.
Reminder: never leave the laser cutter while it's running!
